####################### Admin Panel
Sign up new user POST
/adminpanel/registration

Delete user DELETE
/adminpanel/{id}/rem/account

Add permission to user PUT
/adminpanel/{id}/add/{permission}

Remove permission to user PUT
/adminpanel/{id}/rem/{permission}

Get list of users with specific permission GET
/adminpanel/{permission}

####################### User panel

Create new db record POST
/create

Get full db record list GET
/clients

Get record by its id GET
/clients/{id}

Update record PUT
/clients/{id}

Delete record DELETE
/clients/{id}